Package: gitProfiler
Title: Git Repository Analysis for Developer Profiling and Anomaly Detection
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Alina", "Gribanova", email = "gribanovaalya@mail.ru", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Anna", "Erofeeva", role = "aut"),
    person("Tatyana", "Maksimova", role = "aut")
  )
Description: Provides tools for extracting and analyzing Git repository data,
    building behavioral developer profiles, detecting anomalies in commit patterns,
    and generating team metrics. Designed for HR and team leads to
    objectively evaluate developer contributions and optimize team composition.
